==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Carbuncled
<hw>Car"bun*cled</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Set
with carbuncles.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>He has deserves it [armor], were it <qex>carbuncled</qex>⟦br⟧
Like holy Phabus' car.</q> <rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Affected with a carbuncle or carbuncles; marked with
red sores; pimpled and blotched.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧A <xex>carbuncled</xex>
face.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Brome.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Carbuncular</ent>⟦br⟧
